  "strategy": [
    "Alternate between short forward moves and scanning rotations to maximize blue object detection.",
    "Use commit states to enforce persistence in forward and rotation actions, preventing oscillations.",
    "On blue_seen, immediately switch to a dedicated approach sequence (move_to_blue_commit) and do not return to exploration unless blue is lost.",
    "On blue_close, always stop to avoid collision and complete the task.",
    "After obstacle detection, use recovery (backward or rotate) and scan states before resuming exploration.",
    "Never allow move_forward after obstacle_front without a recovery state.",
    "Allow stop as a controllable action in blue approach/close states for safe task completion.",
